          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Hotel Advertising Transparency Act of 20</b><strong>22</strong><br> <br> This bill requires hotels, and other places of short-term lodging, to include all required fees in the advertised rate.</p> <p>This requirement may be enforced by the Federal Trade Commission, state attorneys general, and other authorized state officials.</p>]]>
        </text>
